{"tid":1697472,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"［狐狸尾巴］葉國謙：11月17日仲有暴力事件，行會或推新選舉條例，區選會暫停至新例通過為止","createTime":"2019-11-07T01:22:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-24T23:10:20.000Z","uid":48083,"like":7,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":35,"replies":[{"pid":"e5e3bc6a0b87c60979c627e1f2d68b7008c59c7b","tid":1697472,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T01:22:51.000Z","msg":"華爾街狠人<br />\n<br />\n（突發！港共政權露出狐狸尾巴！！！）建制派葉國謙今朝喺電台表示：如果11月17日還出現暴力事件，應該會取消11月24日的區議會選舉<br />\n<br />\n狠人啱啱聽到，行會成員+民建聯立法會黨團召集人葉國謙在電台節目《千禧年代》表示：琴日何君堯遇襲事件，反映建制派候選人及助手被針對，對選舉唔公平，選舉委員會視乎實際情況是否應該繼續11月24日的區議會選舉，主持問佢：「理論上係唔係根據選舉條例最多延期14日再舉行？」<br />\n<br />\n葉國謙：「照現時情況，延遲14日再選的意思不大，暴力情況會繼續發生，行會有機會推動新嘅法案，咁區議會選舉會暫時停頓，直至立法會通過新嘅選舉條例！」<br />\n<br />\n片段：<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/rthkpau/videos/529001374588932\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Frthkpau%2Fvideos%2F529001374588932&d=40Eeu%2FLL1847%2FNonScroNSvt59O44HeJS3%2BtxtDyp5g%3D&h=bcda277d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/rthkpau/videos/529001374588932</a>"},{"pid":"42ea7392be300ab160060a61b78961f65a83a0fc","tid":1697472,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T01:24:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3e767eb78c9fac94452a53cf49b1175a266a93b6","tid":1697472,"uid":14897,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T01:29:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f1509c71e3ced9fd94b4a172bd2231dd9a0a0710","tid":1697472,"uid":36134,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T01:32:42.000Z","msg":"做場大龍鳳 都估撚到你地啦<br />\n自編自導自演 仲要唔敢玩大d <br />\n個傷口仲細過我粒菲子<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"32423d1d2831c195e470ef5b2deba6eb0e0ebc50","tid":16